00:54:26,573 --> 00:54:31,010
祈祷在此次愚蠢的袭击中受害者早日康复@
and to pray for the recovery of the victims of this senseless attack.

627
00:54:31,978 --> 00:54:33,855
新芬党对此表示愤慨
Sinn Fein are outraged,

628
