- I know the deal. - You are the victim of a crime.

650
00:56:20,879 --> 00:56:23,381
那会影响你所作的分析
And that does not make for the best analysis

651
00:56:23,465 --> 00:56:25,508
就算你熟知恐怖主义也不行
even if you knew something about terrorism,

652
00:56:25,592 --> 00:56:26,801
何况你还不了解
which you do not.

653
00:56:26,885 --> 00:56:29,304
我已经派了专家去调查
I have guys on it, guys who know something about the IRA.

654
00:56:29,387 --> 00:56:31,765
- 马蒂，我不是来…  - 这不是海军情报
- Marty, I am not standing here... - This is not naval intelligence.

655
00:56:31,890 --> 00:56:35,101
马蒂，我不是来求你
Marty, I am not standing here with my hat in my hand!

656
00:56:35,602 --> 00:56:38,104
我是在要求复职
I am telling you, I want back in.

657
00:56:38,605 --> 00:56:39,689
杰克？
Jack?

658
00:56:39,773 --> 00:56:40,815
先生
Sir.

659
00:56:40,940 --> 00:56:42,859
- 幸好莎莉没事  - 谢谢你
- Thank God about Sally. - Thank you.

660
00:56:42,942 --> 00:56:45,236
爱丽丝和我终于可以放心
Alice and I are relieved beyond words.

661
00:56:46,780 --> 00:56:49,407
- 你最近睡得还好吗？  - 没怎么睡，先生
- You manage any sleep? - Not much, sir.

662
00:56:51,618 --> 00:56:53,453
似乎我打扰你们了
I'm interrupting something.

663
00:56:54,662 --> 00:56:55,789
你该不会在向他说
You were explaining to Jack

664
00:56:55,914 --> 00:56:58,792
没有他，我们能做得更好
about how we'd be better off without him around here,

665
00:57:00,335 --> 00:57:02,629
