672
00:57:22,190 --> 00:57:23,233
你好
Well.

673
00:57:23,316 --> 00:57:24,317
萝丝
Rose.

674
00:57:24,442 --> 00:57:27,112
你的气色比我想像中好多了
I have to say, you're looking better than I expected.

675
00:57:27,195 --> 00:57:28,446
那只是表面
It's an illusion, I'm afraid.

676
00:57:28,530 --> 00:57:30,406
我知道
Of course, it would have to be, wouldn't it?

677
00:57:30,490 --> 00:57:32,325
真高兴再看见你
Well, it's good to see you again regardless.

678
00:57:32,450 --> 00:57:33,576
我也是
You, too.

679
00:57:33,660 --> 00:57:35,288
这是你的办公位@
Look, we've carved a niche for you,

680
00:57:35,646 --> 00:57:38,030
这些是你的晚间功课
and here's your night-table reading.

681
00:57:38,105 --> 00:57:38,523
（爱国者）

682
00:57:38,540 --> 00:57:39,791
老天
Oh, my.

