688
00:58:35,221 --> 00:58:36,347
这边
This way.

689
00:58:36,681 --> 00:58:37,891
过来
Over here.

690
00:58:39,934 --> 00:58:41,519
早上好，先生，请熄火
Good morning, sir. Cut the engine, please.

691
00:58:41,603 --> 00:58:44,606
能看你的证件吗？
Can I see some form of identification, please?

692
00:58:45,064 --> 00:58:48,025
