（英国人滚出去）

693
00:59:09,920 --> 00:59:11,522
你有看球赛吗？@
Did you see the game, then?

694
00:59:11,671 --> 00:59:12,920
有，还不错
Yeah. It was all right.

695
01:00:01,140 --> 01:00:02,850
什么事？
What the hell?

696
01:00:02,934 --> 01:00:04,143
都不许动！
Nobody move!

697
01:00:05,270 --> 01:00:06,437
将他们拉起来
Get them up!

698
01:00:10,984 --> 01:00:12,151
早上好
Morning.

699
01:00:13,486 --> 01:00:16,030
凯文・奥唐纳，资深爱尔兰共和军战略家
Kevin O'Donnell, longtime IRA strategist,

700
01:00:16,114 --> 01:00:17,573
米勒家的朋友
friend of the Miller family.

701
01:00:17,657 --> 01:00:20,076
蒂莫西・米勒在79年被杀时他在场
He was there when Timothy Miller was killed, '79.

702
01:00:20,159 --> 01:00:22,870
他之后便照顾他两个儿子，肖恩和帕特里克
Looked after his boys, Sean and Patrick.

703
01:00:23,538 --> 01:00:25,248
这是近照
This photo's not a year old.

704
01:00:25,330 --> 01:00:27,108
若我们能找到奥唐纳@
I think if we could find O'Donnell,

