Think it's going to turn up registered?

710
01:00:37,802 --> 01:00:39,095
我只是问一下
I'm asking a question.

711
01:00:39,178 --> 01:00:40,805
- 混蛋  - 什么事
- Son of a bitch. - What?

712
01:00:44,892 --> 01:00:46,227
你们看
Look, um...

713
01:00:48,980 --> 01:00:50,481
