No, no, no, no, look.

723
01:01:13,588 --> 01:01:17,133
爱尔兰共和军旅指挥官，吉米・欧莱奥登
We've got Brigade Commander of the IRA, Jimmy O'Reardon,

724
01:01:17,216 --> 01:01:20,011
