725
01:01:20,094 --> 01:01:21,512
非常专业
Very professional.

726
01:01:21,929 --> 01:01:24,432
那是农舍事件多久后？
And that was... How long after the farmhouse?

727
01:01:24,515 --> 01:01:25,600
同一天
Same day.

728
01:01:26,392 --> 01:01:27,518
同一天
Same day.

729
