or some ultraviolent faction of the IRA...

747
01:03:48,019 --> 01:03:49,633
擅自行动呢？
fighting the cause their way?

748
01:03:50,536 --> 01:03:52,163
对，对，对
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.

749
01:03:52,546 --> 01:03:55,806
