01:19:03,089 --> 01:19:04,240
这样你也相信？
and you believe him?

937
01:19:06,660 --> 01:19:09,913
我没有跟他说我找的是女人
I didn't tell him I was looking for a girl, Marty.

938
01:19:13,917 --> 01:19:17,086
（珍本书协会）

939
01:19:41,111 --> 01:19:42,279
警官？
Sarge?

940
01:19:43,155 --> 01:19:45,031
过来看看这个
Come and look at this.

941
01:19:57,168 --> 01:19:58,211
（斯塔电力有限公司，1917年）

942
01:19:58,378 --> 01:20:00,338
我其实也是一名书虫
Bit of a bookworm meself,

943
01:20:00,464 --> 01:20:02,340
虽然看起来不像
not that you'd know it to look at me.

944
01:20:02,630 --> 01:20:03,964
你喜欢什么类型的书？
What's your passion, then?

945
01:20:04,251 --> 01:20:06,340
悬疑小说？间谍小说？
Mysteries? Spy novels?

946
01:20:06,803 --> 01:20:08,013
伊恩・弗莱明读过吗？
Familiar with Ian Fleming, are you?

947
01:20:08,138 --> 01:20:09,806
这是一家珍品书店
This is a rare book shop.

948
01:20:09,890 --> 01:20:11,141
珍品书？
Rare books?

949
01:20:11,850 --> 01:20:13,143
的确很少见
Yeah, so they are.

950
01:20:13,226 --> 01:20:15,604
你找到问题了吗？不然我找别人了
Can you locate the problem, or do I have to call someone else?

951
01:20:15,687 --> 01:20:16,980
找到了
Already have.

952
01:20:17,063 --> 01:20:20,066
整座楼的电线都是在战前铺设的
The wiring in this whole place dates from before the war.

953
01:20:20,150 --> 01:20:21,151
是一战前
The first war.

954
01:20:21,234 --> 01:20:24,237
对我们电力行业来说也很罕见
It's what we call, in the electrical business, rare.

955
01:20:24,321 --> 01:20:25,489
你能修好吗？
Yes. Can you fix it?

956
01:20:25,572 --> 01:20:27,282
当然可以
Oh, sure. I can fix it.

957
01:20:27,365 --> 01:20:28,658
不过你付得起帐吗？
Can you afford it? That's the question.

958
01:20:28,742 --> 01:20:30,160
你只管修好了
Just fix it.

959
01:20:39,085 --> 01:20:40,212
哎哟
Hello.

960
01:20:40,670 --> 01:20:42,005
他看见了吗？
He's seen it, hasn't he?

961
01:20:42,088 --> 01:20:43,173
我不知道
I don't know.

962
01:20:45,842 --> 01:20:47,219
他发现了
He's got it. Look.

963
01:20:48,887 --> 01:20:50,847
这是什么？
Here, what do you make of this?

964
01:20:52,224 --> 01:20:53,350
我…
I...

965
01:20:56,353 --> 01:20:57,687
我不知道
I have no idea.

966
01:20:58,855 --> 01:20:59,940
该死
Damn!

967
01:21:03,068 --> 01:21:05,612
我现在要出去一下
I have to go out now for a few minutes

968
01:21:06,530 --> 01:21:08,198
要送几本书
to deliver some books.

969
01:21:09,574 --> 01:21:10,992
请你继续修吧
Please keep about your repairs.

970
01:21:11,076 --> 01:21:13,787
这得花一周才能完成，别急
I'll be here all week, guv. Don't worry.

971
01:21:19,709 --> 01:21:22,211
（珍本书）

972
01:21:25,131 --> 01:21:27,133
（库利书店）

973
01:21:55,495 --> 01:21:56,913
我要抓到他
He's mine!

974
01:22:31,489 --> 01:22:32,616
该死
Damn!

975
01:22:48,048 --> 01:22:50,467
在白宫的晚宴没问题
Dinner at the White House is no problem.

976
01:22:50,842 --> 01:22:52,010
那问题是什么？
What is the problem?

977
01:22:52,135 --> 01:22:54,971
没问题，我们只是那天没时间
No problem, we're just running out of dates.

978
01:22:55,555 --> 01:22:57,223
我们可以这么做
Yes. We could do that.

979
01:22:57,307 --> 01:22:58,850
把这件事挪到那天
Move that to there,

980
01:22:58,975 --> 01:23:02,646
这样14号就有空了
which would leave us the 14th?

981
01:23:03,521 --> 01:23:04,564
14号
The 14th.

982
01:23:04,640 --> 01:23:05,542
杰弗里
Geoffrey,

983
01:23:05,886 --> 01:23:09,668
向约翰・雷恩确认一下授勋晚宴的事宜
let's check with John Ryan about scheduling a presentation dinner

984
01:23:09,746 --> 01:23:12,686
在华盛顿使馆的时间是…
at our embassy in Washington on the...

985
01:23:13,198 --> 01:23:14,324
14号
14th.

986
01:23:15,408 --> 01:23:16,701
14号
The 14th.

987
01:23:18,536 --> 01:23:21,748
我们再核对一下，好让我有个清楚的概念
So, let's go over this again so I can get it clear.

988
01:23:21,831 --> 01:23:24,000
我们先在华盛顿白宫…
We start in Washington with the White House...

989
01:23:28,171 --> 01:23:29,255
我是杰弗里・沃特金斯
Geoffrey Watkins.

990
01:23:29,339 --> 01:23:32,717
抱歉，我要找泰特斯先生
Oh, I beg your pardon. I'm trying to reach Mr. Titus.

991
01:23:33,551 --> 01:23:35,595
请问这分机是2691吗？
Is that extension 2691?

992
01:23:35,887 --> 01:23:37,347
不是，是2619
No, this is 2619.

993
01:23:37,430 --> 01:23:39,182
非常抱歉
I'm terribly sorry.

994
01:23:49,234 --> 01:23:50,944
你起来做什么？快回去睡觉
What are you doing up? Go back to bed.

995
01:23:51,027 --> 01:23:53,655
我想在她醒来时在她身旁
I wanted to be there when she wakes up.

996
01:23:55,240 --> 01:23:56,991
我和你一起去，然后我坐计程车回来
I'll go with you, and then I'll take a cab back.

997
01:23:57,075 --> 01:23:58,201
好吧
Okay.

998
01:24:00,203 --> 01:24:01,287
喂？（请找约翰・雷恩爵士）
Hello?

999
01:24:02,414 --> 01:24:03,915
请稍等
Yes. Just a minute.

1000
01:24:04,082 --> 01:24:05,583
找你的
It's for you,

1001
01:24:06,042 --> 01:24:07,252
约翰爵士
Sir John.

1002
01:24:08,420 --> 01:24:09,587
你好？
Hello?

1003
01:24:12,716 --> 01:24:13,842
对不起，先生
Excuse me, sir.

1004
01:24:13,925 --> 01:24:17,011
雷恩先生当晚有庆祝活动，不能改期了
Mr. Ryan has a special celebration that evening that he can't change.

1005
01:24:17,095 --> 01:24:18,972
他想邀请你参加
He wondered if you might care to join them.

1006
01:24:19,055 --> 01:24:20,807
在哪，他家里吗？
Where, at his house?

1007
01:24:21,307 --> 01:24:22,600
是的，先生
Yes, sir.

1008
01:24:25,895 --> 01:24:27,105
有何不可？
Why not?

1009
01:24:38,575 --> 01:24:40,869
这是我们八天前在柏林拍的
We shot this eight days ago in Berlin.

1010
01:24:42,746 --> 01:24:43,913
一
One,

1011
01:24:44,622 --> 01:24:45,790
二
two,

1012
01:24:46,124 --> 01:24:48,668
三，共四位英国人和他一起
three, four Brits traveling with him.

1013
01:24:49,627 --> 01:24:50,920
轻型武器
Light arms.

1014
01:24:52,797 --> 01:24:54,549
重型武器在车内
The heavy stuff's in the cars.

1015
01:24:54,630 --> 01:24:55,851
他是德国人
He's German,

1016
01:24:56,386 --> 01:24:57,300
他也是
he's German.

1017
01:24:57,427 --> 01:24:59,179
肖恩，你对这不感兴趣吗？
This boring you, Sean?

1018
01:24:59,637 --> 01:25:01,431
四个，加起来总共六个
Four, six altogether.

1019
01:25:02,599 --> 01:25:05,852
霍姆斯飞去华盛顿，也应该是同样的保安人员
Should be the same security when Holmes flies to Washington.

1020
01:25:05,977 --> 01:25:08,813
我们必须找到他周围没有保安人员的空隙
We've got to find the moment when he's unprotected.

1021
01:25:09,147 --> 01:25:13,109
华盛顿四天，纽约一天
Four days in Washington, one day in New York.

1022
01:25:14,319 --> 01:25:15,612
购物
Shopping.

1023
01:25:29,834 --> 01:25:32,796
没错 两个高加索人
Yeah. Two Caucasians.

1024
01:25:33,671 --> 01:25:35,840
看看那个戴帽子的人
Take a look at the one with the hat.

1025
01:25:38,301 --> 01:25:40,136
他胳膊有点发红
His arms look a little pink.

1026
01:25:40,970 --> 01:25:43,181
太阳晒伤的，一定是刚来的
Sunburn. New arrival.

1027
01:25:59,823 --> 01:26:01,658
你觉得呢？同一个人？
What do you think? Same guy?

1028
01:26:04,911 --> 01:26:07,205
那个珍本书商，丹尼斯库利
That rare book dealer, Dennis Cooley,

1029
01:26:08,039 --> 01:26:09,374
他是秃头
he's bald.

1030
01:26:12,210 --> 01:26:15,348
营地里可能有女人@
Now, it's possible there could be a woman in some of these camps,

1031
01:26:17,006 --> 01:26:19,843
但是她和库利一起出现…
but with her and Cooley in the same place,

1032
01:26:22,053 --> 01:26:23,721
如果那是库利
if that is Cooley,

1033
01:26:23,930 --> 01:26:26,391
就应该不只是巧合
the odds of coincidence are dropping fast.

1034
01:26:29,227 --> 01:26:32,272
但我还不确定，我还没有办法…
Still, I don't know. There's no way I can be...

1035
01:26:34,774 --> 01:26:36,568
绝对肯定
absolutely certain.

1036
01:26:37,193 --> 01:26:38,528
拜托你，杰克
Excuse me, Jack.

1037
01:26:39,279 --> 01:26:42,866
生命中有能完全肯定的事吗？
Tell me one thing in life that is absolutely for certain.

1038
01:26:45,368 --> 01:26:46,870
我女儿的爱
My daughter's love.

1039
01:26:49,747 --> 01:26:52,292
我要知道的是你的最佳臆测
What I need to hear from you is your best guess,

1040
01:26:52,375 --> 01:26:54,085
我想我知道了
and I think I've heard it.

1041
01:26:59,215 --> 01:27:00,550
没错吧？
Haven't I?

1042
01:27:11,144 --> 01:27:13,646
那些混蛋夺走了我的书店
The bastards took away my book shop.

1043
01:27:14,063 --> 01:27:15,690
他们搬走了我的书！
They took away my books!

1044
01:27:15,773 --> 01:27:17,859
丹尼斯，你不能来这里
I'm sorry, Dennis. You can't come.

1045
01:27:17,942 --> 01:27:19,903
你没有经过训练
You haven't got the training,

1046
01:27:20,403 --> 01:27:22,363
这项任务很复杂的
and this mission's going to be very messy.

1047
01:27:22,447 --> 01:27:24,073
我会开枪
I can fire a gun.

1048
01:27:48,473 --> 01:27:49,974
抱歉，丹尼斯
Sorry, Dennis.

1049
01:28:21,798 --> 01:28:23,091
你要带我去哪，马蒂？
Where are you taking me, Marty?

1050
01:28:23,174 --> 01:28:25,510
是你带我们来的，杰克
It's you who've taken us, Jack...

1051
01:28:26,636 --> 01:28:28,721
卫星现在已进入目的地区域
Satellite now entering target area.

1052
01:28:28,805 --> 01:28:30,306
进入战斗
into battle.

1053
01:28:30,890 --> 01:28:31,975
长官
Sir.

1054
01:28:32,809 --> 01:28:34,477
放大第四区域
Enlargement sector four.

1055
01:28:42,819 --> 01:28:45,196
空军接近目的地区域
Airborne support approaching target area.

1056
01:28:45,321 --> 01:28:48,157
预计到达时间35秒
ETA, 35 seconds.

1057
01:29:21,941 --> 01:29:23,693
地面是空降特勤队
SAS team on ground.

1058
01:29:38,374 --> 01:29:40,543
- 放大第18营  - 正在放大
- Enlarge camp 18. - Enlarging.

1059
01:29:42,545 --> 01:29:45,214
- 放大第一目标  - 正在放大
- Enlarge primary target. - Enlarging.

1060
01:29:53,639 --> 01:29:55,099
杀得漂亮
That is a kill.

1061
01:29:59,395 --> 01:30:02,231
收到，行动
Roger, roger. It's go, go, go.

1062
01:30:08,946 --> 01:30:10,907
目标已被消灭
Targets have been neutralized.

1063
01:30:22,460 --> 01:30:24,337
空军支援队正在接近
Airborne support approaching.

1064
01:30:26,798 --> 01:30:28,591
放大第五区域
Enlarge sector five.

1065
01:30:37,474 --> 01:30:39,268
（即时传送）

1066
01:30:45,983 --> 01:30:47,401
描述第二区域
Angle sector two.

1067
01:30:47,485 --> 01:30:48,986
第二区域
Sector two.

1068
01:30:49,320 --> 01:30:50,779
（状态：即时）

1069
01:30:54,826 --> 01:30:56,327
空降特勤队撤退
SAS team withdrawing.

1070
01:31:06,504 --> 01:31:08,965
影像结束
Keyhole is passing out of visual.

1071
01:31:22,478 --> 01:31:23,813
结束了
It's over.

1072
01:31:54,385 --> 01:31:55,678
来吧，宝贝
Come on, honey.

1073
01:31:57,013 --> 01:31:58,097
跳
Jump.

1074
01:32:05,396 --> 01:32:06,439
你看
See?

1075
01:32:14,738 --> 01:32:17,241
（莎莉，欢迎回家）

1076
01:32:17,408 --> 01:32:19,035
谢谢
Appreciate it. Thanks.

1077
01:32:27,710 --> 01:32:29,212
巡逻一组，没有情况
Surveillance team one, all clear.

1078
01:32:30,880 --> 01:32:31,881
收到
Roger that.

1079
01:32:31,964 --> 01:32:34,050
你的手下需要喝杯咖啡吗？
You sure your men outside wouldn't like some coffee?

1080
01:32:34,133 --> 01:32:35,593
不用了，雷恩夫人
No, thank you, Mrs. Ryan. They'll be just fine.

1081
01:32:35,718 --> 01:32:36,761
好吧
Okay.

1082
01:32:36,886 --> 01:32:38,471
我想谢谢你，雷恩小姐
And I'd to thank you, Miss Ryan,

1083
01:32:38,554 --> 01:32:40,932
谢谢你邀请我们参加庆祝会
for allowing us to impose upon your homecoming.

1084
01:32:41,057 --> 01:32:43,476
你是一位美丽优雅的女孩
You're a beautiful and gracious young lady.

1085
01:32:43,559 --> 01:32:46,812
认识你是我莫大的荣幸
And it's my distinct pleasure to make your acquaintance.

1086
01:32:47,063 --> 01:32:48,314
不客气
You're welcome.

1087
01:32:50,060 --> 01:32:53,106
我想晚宴后再颁发勋章，如果你没有意见的话
I thought I might make the presentation after dinner, if you agree.

1088
01:32:53,444 --> 01:32:54,737
当然
Oh, sure.

1089
01:32:55,780 --> 01:32:57,406
你现在想看看吗？
Would you like to see it now?

1090
01:32:57,490 --> 01:32:58,908
杰弗里
Geoffrey...

1091
01:33:03,788 --> 01:33:05,289
- 天啊，非常漂亮  - 很漂亮
- Oh, my. That's very nice. - It's lovely.

1092
01:33:05,414 --> 01:33:07,750
我不是已经给过你一个了吗？
Didn't I already give you one of those?

1093
01:33:12,171 --> 01:33:13,798
请大家自便
Help yourselves.

1094
01:33:22,932 --> 01:33:25,851
这是你的第二块蛋糕了吧，小宝贝？
Is that your second piece of cake, my little sweetie?

1095
01:33:27,353 --> 01:33:28,771
杰克，厕所在哪？
Where's the bathroom, Jack?

1096
01:33:28,854 --> 01:33:31,107
- 二楼左手边  - 谢谢
- Second door on the left. - Thank you.

1097
01:33:31,440 --> 01:33:32,566
谁还要点咖啡？
More coffee, anyone?

1098
01:33:32,650 --> 01:33:33,943
我要
I'd love some.

1099
01:33:35,444 --> 01:33:36,612
失陪一下
Excuse me.

1100
01:33:37,530 --> 01:33:38,823
打雷了
Here it comes.

1101
01:33:39,782 --> 01:33:40,866
厕所？
Bathroom?

1102
01:33:42,785 --> 01:33:44,120
- 里面有人  - 不，不是那间
- Someone in there. - No, that's not it.

1103
01:33:44,203 --> 01:33:45,997
那是地下室
That's the basement.

1104
01:33:54,880 --> 01:33:55,965
喂？
Hello?

1105
01:33:56,048 --> 01:33:57,174
杰克？我是马蒂
Jack? Marty.

1106
01:33:57,300 --> 01:33:59,135
马蒂，有什么事吗？
Marty. What's going on?

1107
01:33:59,302 --> 01:34:00,594
很抱歉打扰了你的派对
I'm sorry to interrupt your party,

1108
01:34:00,678 --> 01:34:02,346
但你应该想尽快知道这消息
but I thought you'd like to know right away.

1109
01:34:02,972 --> 01:34:05,641
空降特勤队已经确认了丹尼斯・库利的尸体
SAS just made positive ID on Dennis Cooley.

1110
01:34:05,891 --> 01:34:07,476
其他人呢？
What about the others?

1111
01:34:07,560 --> 01:34:09,478
尸体面目全非
Well, it was pretty messy, as it turns out.

1112
01:34:09,645 --> 01:34:12,815
需要48小时才能做出牙齿鉴定
It's going to take 48 hours to verify the dental records,

1113
01:34:13,357 --> 01:34:15,401
他们正在努力辨认
but they're keeping right on it.

1114
01:34:16,527 --> 01:34:17,653
糟糕
Oh, great.

1115
01:34:17,820 --> 01:34:18,904
怎么了？
What?

1116
01:34:19,322 --> 01:34:21,449
现在正打雷，屋里停电了
The storm just knocked out the power here to the house.

1117
01:34:21,532 --> 01:34:22,533
我要去点一些蜡烛
I've got to light some candles.

1118
01:34:22,658 --> 01:34:24,493
我也为你点一支
I'll light one for you, too.

1119
01:34:24,827 --> 01:34:26,329
好，马蒂，谢谢
Okay, Marty. Thanks.

1120
01:34:28,581 --> 01:34:29,832
来了
Here we go.

1121
01:34:29,999 --> 01:34:31,834
怎么，你忘了交电费吗，凯西？
What, forget to pay your bill, Cath?

1122
01:34:31,917 --> 01:34:34,003
罗伯，你很幽默
Robert. Very funny.

1123
01:34:34,503 --> 01:34:35,546
大家都没事吧？
Everyone all right?

1124
01:34:35,671 --> 01:34:38,049
- 我们很好，杰克  - 这样感觉更棒
- We're fine, Jack. - We like it better this way.

1125
01:34:38,424 --> 01:34:40,301
这种情况可不常发生，霍姆斯公爵
This doesn't happen very often, Lord Holmes.

1126
01:34:40,384 --> 01:34:42,845
只有皇室人员来参加晚宴才会出现这种情况
Only when we have royalty over for dinner.

1127
01:34:45,014 --> 01:34:46,724
我知道您了解的
I knew you'd understand.

1128
01:34:50,019 --> 01:34:51,354
怎么了？
Something wrong?

1129
01:34:51,560 --> 01:34:52,791
跟我来好吗？@
Come with me, will you?

1130
01:34:52,943 --> 01:34:54,390
妈妈，我必须这样吗？
Mom, do I have to?

1131
01:34:56,025 --> 01:34:58,819
如果停电是因为雷电，那么船库也应该停电
If the storm had knocked out the lights, they'd be out in the boathouse, too.

1132
01:34:58,903 --> 01:34:59,862
所以呢？
So?

1133
01:34:59,945 --> 01:35:03,783
电力来自街上，再接来这里
Power comes in from the street, and then branches off to here.

1134
01:35:05,534 --> 01:35:06,577
上帝
Jesus.

1135
01:35:09,372 --> 01:35:11,290
我是雷恩，请问有外交安全局的探员吗？
This is Ryan. Any DSS agent?

1136
01:35:12,375 --> 01:35:14,794
外交安全局的探员请回话，我是雷恩
Any DSS agent, this is Ryan.

1137
01:35:15,044 --> 01:35:17,129
有马里兰州州警吗？有人吗？
Maryland troopers? Anyone?

1138
01:35:18,089 --> 01:35:19,715
有人听到我说话吗？
Is anyone reading me?

1139
01:35:20,424 --> 01:35:21,634
有人吗？
Anybody?

1140
01:35:23,094 --> 01:35:25,679
电来的时候我能再下来吗？
Can I come back down when the lights are on?

1141
01:35:25,763 --> 01:35:27,640
不行，小宝贝，你必须睡觉
No, sweetie-pie. You've got to get some sleep.

1142
01:35:27,723 --> 01:35:29,266
已经很晚了
It's very late.

1143
01:35:29,892 --> 01:35:31,102
可恶
Goddamn.

1144
01:35:36,107 --> 01:35:37,400
不要告诉他们
Don't tell me.

1145
01:35:37,942 --> 01:35:39,443
风暴很大
Quite a storm.

1146
01:35:44,657 --> 01:35:47,034
不要碰我，你在做什么？
Take your hands off me. What the hell do you think you're doing?

1147
01:35:47,118 --> 01:35:48,119
杰克
Jack.

1148
01:35:52,998 --> 01:35:54,166
枪
Gun.

1149
01:35:55,418 --> 01:35:56,502
杰克
Jack.

1150
01:36:08,681 --> 01:36:10,307
不要动
Stay right there.

1151
01:36:10,933 --> 01:36:12,101
该死
Shit.

1152
01:36:12,977 --> 01:36:14,520
罗伯，这边
Rob, over here.

1153
01:36:14,978 --> 01:36:16,647
（开）
（关）

1154
01:36:20,943 --> 01:36:22,945
计划是什么？要来多少人？
What's the plan? How many are coming?

1155
01:36:23,028 --> 01:36:24,196
肖恩・米勒在哪？
Where's Sean Miller?

1156
01:36:24,280 --> 01:36:26,282
我不懂你在讲什么
I don't know what you're talking about.

1157
01:36:26,365 --> 01:36:27,700
把枪给我
Give me the gun.

1158
01:36:32,329 --> 01:36:33,914
五或六个？
Five? Six?

1159
01:36:33,998 --> 01:36:35,374
可能更多
I don't know. Maybe more.

1160
01:36:35,740 --> 01:36:38,055
我去找其他人，不要开灯
I'll get the others. Don't turn on the lights.

1161
01:36:45,968 --> 01:36:47,928
拿着这个，快去地下室
Take this. Get down in the basement quick.

1162
01:36:48,012 --> 01:36:49,513
- 凯西和莎莉在哪儿？  - 她们在楼上
- Where's Cathy and Sally? - They're upstairs.

1163
01:36:49,638 --> 01:36:50,806
- 她在哄莎莉睡觉  - 快走
- She's putting Sally to bed. - Go.

1164
01:36:50,890 --> 01:36:52,349
怎么了？
What's wrong?

1165
01:37:20,544 --> 01:37:22,713
来吧，雷恩，现身吧
Come on, Ryan. Show yourself.

1166
01:37:28,219 --> 01:37:29,637
安妮特，楼上
Annette, upstairs.

1167
01:37:29,720 --> 01:37:30,888
好
Right.

1168
01:37:47,613 --> 01:37:49,365
跟我来，宝贝，快
Come on, sweetie, come on.

1169
01:37:50,115 --> 01:37:51,825
怎么了，妈妈？
What's wrong, Mommy?

1170
01:37:54,370 --> 01:37:56,539
你帮我爬到凳子上去
Now, you've got to help me. Climb up on the stool.

1171
01:37:56,622 --> 01:37:58,582
上面有一支猎枪
There's a shotgun there.

1172
01:38:11,554 --> 01:38:14,723
杰克，你把子弹放哪里了？
Oh, God, Jack, what did you do with the shells?

1173
01:38:18,894 --> 01:38:20,271
走，走
Go, go, go.

1174
01:39:10,613 --> 01:39:11,864
- 快趴下  - 妈妈
- Get down. - Mommy!

1175
01:39:11,947 --> 01:39:12,990
继续
Go on.

1176
01:39:33,552 --> 01:39:34,637
进去
Get back.

1177
01:39:47,358 --> 01:39:49,193
你们没事吧？莎莉在哪？
You all right? Where's Sally?

1178
01:39:49,318 --> 01:39:50,694
- 爸爸  - 莎莉
- Daddy. - Sally.

1179
01:39:51,236 --> 01:39:52,655
没事了，亲爱的
It's okay, honey.

1180
01:39:55,699 --> 01:39:56,992
跟我来
Come on.

1181
01:40:19,390 --> 01:40:22,726
宝贝，你一定要安静
Honey, you've just got to be real quiet. Real quiet.

1182
01:40:41,578 --> 01:40:42,788
找到你了
Gotcha.

1183
01:41:10,899 --> 01:41:12,109
老天
Christ.

1184
01:41:14,778 --> 01:41:15,988
抱紧了
Hold on.

1185
01:41:20,993 --> 01:41:22,619
来吧
Come on, come on.

1186
01:41:39,803 --> 01:41:42,723
你什么意思？谁联系不上了？
What are you talking about? Who is off the air?

1187
01:41:42,806 --> 01:41:44,933
外交安全局，马里兰州州警，所有人
DSS, state troopers, everyone.

1188
01:41:45,142 --> 01:41:46,769
保安公司…
The security company...

1189
01:41:47,352 --> 01:41:49,980
马上帮我接人质救援小组
Get me Hostage Rescue at Quantico now.

1190
01:41:54,985 --> 01:41:57,154
罗伯！开门
Robby! Open up.

1191
01:41:58,363 --> 01:42:00,115
- 罗伯，是我们  - 杰克？
- Robby, it's us. - Jack?

1192
01:42:03,160 --> 01:42:04,888
- 他们在外面  - 肖恩，冷静
- They're outside. - Sean, cool it.

1193
01:42:04,962 --> 01:42:08,120
我们目标是皇室，我们拿着尸体可换不了赎金
It's the royal we want. We can't ransom a dead body.

1194
01:42:10,834 --> 01:42:12,419
到处都是他们的人
They're all over the place, man.

1195
01:42:12,503 --> 01:42:14,004
抱紧我
Stay close to me.

1196
01:42:17,299 --> 01:42:19,426
你们准备怎么逃走？
How were you going to get away, huh?

1197
01:42:19,510 --> 01:42:20,969
要我在膝盖上补一枪吗？
Want to go for the other knee?

1198
01:42:21,053 --> 01:42:23,055
快说
Come on! Come on.

1199
01:42:23,514 --> 01:42:25,682
悬崖底下有船
Boats. Bottom of the cliff.

1200
01:42:25,849 --> 01:42:27,226
那有绳子可以下去
There are ropes.

1201
01:42:28,143 --> 01:42:29,311
凯文
Kevin!

1202
01:43:39,214 --> 01:43:40,757
你杀死他了
You killed him!

1203
01:44:34,478 --> 01:44:36,104
不！肖恩
No, Sean, no!

1204
01:44:36,605 --> 01:44:38,106
我们需要活捉霍姆斯公爵
We need Holmes alive!

1205
01:44:38,273 --> 01:44:39,608
已经不需要了！
We're past that!

1206
01:44:40,025 --> 01:44:41,193
活捉
Alive!

1207
01:44:51,495 --> 01:44:52,788
快走
Come on!

1208
01:45:14,518 --> 01:45:15,686
联系上了吗？
Any contact?

1209
01:45:17,646 --> 01:45:18,730
没有
Still off the air.

1210
01:45:39,876 --> 01:45:41,336
他在那里
There he is!

1211
01:45:51,179 --> 01:45:52,723
蹲下
Stay down there.

1212
01:46:19,249 --> 01:46:21,043
跟我来啊，王八蛋
Come on, you bastards.

1213
01:46:26,590 --> 01:46:28,550
来吧！来吧
Come on! Come on!

1214
01:46:29,760 --> 01:46:31,219
船上只有他一个人
He's alone!

1215
01:46:31,595 --> 01:46:33,930
他把我们从皇室那里引开
He's leading us away from the royal!

1216
01:46:34,056 --> 01:46:35,640
- 调头吧，肖恩  - 不
- Turn around, Sean. - No.

1217
01:46:35,724 --> 01:46:37,184
调头，肖恩！
Turn it round, Sean!

1218
01:46:37,267 --> 01:46:38,477
- 调头，肖恩！  - 不！
- Turn it round, Sean! - No!

1219
01:46:38,560 --> 01:46:39,770
肖恩！
Sean!

1220
01:46:41,438 --> 01:46:44,149
调头！调头！
Turn it round! Turn it round!

1221
01:46:44,232 --> 01:46:46,068
不要管雷恩了！
Forget about Ryan!

1222
01:46:46,568 --> 01:46:48,612
不要破坏行动，兄弟
Don't blow the mission now, boy!

1223
01:46:48,779 --> 01:46:50,572
那不是我的行动！
That's not my mission!

1224
01:46:56,912 --> 01:46:58,580
你这个疯子
You crazy bastard!

1225
01:47:44,876 --> 01:47:46,002
糟糕
Damn!

1226
01:51:17,547 --> 01:51:19,382
吃饱了吗？还是再来点别的
Had enough to eat, honey, or do you want something else?

1227
01:51:19,507 --> 01:51:21,384
- 来点吐司还是…  - 薄煎饼
- Some toast or... - Pancakes.

1228
01:51:21,509 --> 01:51:22,802
没时间做薄煎饼了
There's no time for pancakes, honey.

1229
01:51:22,886 --> 01:51:24,179
要面包还是吐司？
Do you want toast or toast?

1230
01:51:25,388 --> 01:51:26,431
吐司
Toast.

1231
01:51:26,556 --> 01:51:29,225
- 接下电话好吗？  - 我来接吧
- Is somebody going to get that? - I'm getting it.

1232
01:51:29,351 --> 01:51:30,393
莎莉？
Sally?

1233
01:51:31,227 --> 01:51:33,104
喂？对
Hello? It is.

1234
01:51:33,563 --> 01:51:34,689
她在，请稍等
Yeah, hold on a second.

1235
01:51:34,773 --> 01:51:37,233
- 你的背包在哪里？  - 是泽里安医生
- Where's your backpack? - It's Dr. Zaillian.

1236
01:51:37,942 --> 01:51:39,402
- 羊水诊断结果  - 对
- The amnio. - Yeah.

1237
01:51:39,611 --> 01:51:40,779
喂？
Hello?

1238
01:51:41,571 --> 01:51:43,198
不会有事吧？
Is it going to be okay?

1239
01:51:44,282 --> 01:51:47,702
没事的，宝贝，我们就等着结果好了
It's going to be fine, honey. We're just waiting to find out.

1240
01:51:51,081 --> 01:51:52,165
太好了
Great.

1241
01:51:52,248 --> 01:51:54,417
你想要什么果酱？
What do you want on your toast, honey?

1242
01:51:54,542 --> 01:51:55,585
- 草莓？  - 草莓
- Strawberry? - Strawberry.

1243
01:51:55,710 --> 01:51:56,711
等等
Hold on a second.

1244
01:51:56,752 --> 01:51:58,254
（名字）
（男孩女孩）

1245
01:51:58,296 --> 01:51:59,672
想知道是男孩还是女孩吗？
Do you want to know what it is?

1246
01:51:59,756 --> 01:52:00,757
他告诉你了吗？
Did he tell you?

1247
01:52:00,882 --> 01:52:02,675
他问我，所以我又问你
He's asking. I'm asking you.

1248
01:52:02,759 --> 01:52:05,637
你想知道吗？
I don't know. Do you want to know?

1249
01:52:06,096 --> 01:52:07,639
我不知道，你呢？
I don't know. Do you?

1250
01:52:08,390 --> 01:52:11,059
我本来想知道，现在又不确定了
I thought I wanted to know, but now I'm not so sure.

1251
01:52:11,142 --> 01:52:13,353
等一下好吗，我们在商量
Hold on a second. We're discussing it.

1252
01:52:13,436 --> 01:52:15,730
我也是，既想知道又不想知道
Me, neither. I mean, I do and I don't.

1253
01:52:18,608 --> 01:52:19,776
他等着呢
He's waiting.

1254
01:52:25,615 --> 01:52:26,825
好吧
Okay.

1255
01:52:27,575 --> 01:52:28,785
告诉我们
Tell us.

1256
01:52:29,744 --> 01:52:31,079
好吧，告诉我们
Okay, tell us.

1257
01:52:36,501 --> 01:52:37,836
谢谢
Thank you.


